rdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#122950>1:49:35 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: DEX for a warrior - how critical is it?</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">agi is horrible for AC.  3 agi - 1 ac or so.  1 Raw ac = like 1.55 AC or something like that.  so 100 agi is like 20 raw ac.  Plus with aug and shamy buff u get like +100 neways =P</font><P><center><font size="+2" face="impact" color="red"><marquee behavior="alternate" scrollamount="10" width="300">Betharia's Manhoe<br>Everyone's Biznitch</marquee></font></center><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#B8C0C7><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/utrindade.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Trindade</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Master of the Train Pull<br>The HT Bish</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>181</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#122950>4/13/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#122950>8:37:40 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: DEX for a warrior - how critical is it?</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">STAM is the critical stat.<br>
<br>
At low levels, the Str -&gt; Atk bonus's aren't very good. By the time you hit high levels, you'll have over 190 base str from ac/hp items that give str as an extra stat. Shaman buffs will push you to 255 str anyway, don't worry about it.<br>
<br>
Agi is worthless. 3 points of agi = 1 ac. It makes very little difference. Verant says that &quot;agi decreases the amount you get hit and the amount that you get hit for&quot; because yes, agi does increase AC. AC directly affects these two things, but the increase from agi is minute. The only thing to remember is keeping agi above 75 at all times so that you don't incur an AC penalty.<br>
<br>
Dex is another stat that you'll get a lot of from items. I really wouldn't worry about dex. My base as a barbarian is only 70 too, but items push me over 100, and with the right buffs i hit 255. I *DO* notice that as I level I proc more often. I think it's more that as you break certain &quot;barriers&quot; of dex you get an increase in % of procs (100 is an often quoted one, but i have noticed an increase from 140 -&gt; 150. I think 100 -&gt; 110 wouldn't be any different), and that as you level you also get an increase %. I believe level and weapon delay to be more of a significant factor in proc rates than dex (though dex does help).<br>
<br>
At level 60, 10 stam = 60 hp. An ogre with a base stam of 150 sta has an advantage of 270 hp over a barbarian with 105 sta (my starting stat. =/). It's REALLY hard to get your stam up with items. Getting 255 buffed stam as anything but an ogre with 150 sta requires loot from some of the hossest mobs in the game. Sometimes I really wish I had put all my points into sta instead of str... ahhh, newbie days. Even if you are set on being a barbarian for instance, put your points into stam. 130 is still a highly respectable amount of sta (I'd be at 249 sta buffed if I had assigned my stats that way instead of str).<br>
<br>
HP will make more of a difference to you than any other stat. Your &quot;non crucial&quot; stats tend to work themselves out from items.</font><P>Trindade<br>
58th level warrior<br>
Moving 'zig' for great justice<P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#C5C5BA><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub12.ezboard.com/uquizon.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Quizon</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_ball.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Half elf demi-god</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>1455</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#122950>4/13/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#122950>11:41:36 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http://us.st8.yimg.com/store4.yimg.com/I/wickedcoolstuff_1616_9171752 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: DEX for a warrior - how critical is it?</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Hi, super stamina gimp here.  If I remade my char I'd put all my points in sta.<br>
